            <h3>More Ways to Connect</h3>
            <p><a href="http://www.mitef.org/">Discover one of our 28 local entrepreneurial communities &raquo;</a></p>
            <p class="no-margin"><a href="/connect/">Be the first to know</a> as we launch in new countries and markets around the globe.</p>
            <p class="mini no-margin">Interested in <a href="/contact/submit/?type=internationalpartnerships">bringing MIT Technology Review to your local market?</a></p>
          </div>
        </section>

