  <h2>
                  Hacking the Soul            </h2>
  <nav>
          <ul>
                  <li><a href="/featuredstory/528136/searching-for-the-free-will-neuron/">Free Will</a></li>                  <li><a href="/video/528441/eavesdropping-on-neurons/">Video: Measuring Neurons</a></li>                  <li><a href="/video/528401/the-cross-section-of-memory/">Video: Manipulating Memory</a></li>              </ul>
