          <ul>
                  <li><a href="/featuredstory/528226/neurosciences-new-toolbox/">The Technologies</a></li>                  <li><a href="/qa/528156/the-promise-and-perils-of-manipulating-memory/">Q&amp;A: Memories</a></li>                  <li><a href="/featuredstory/528146/shining-light-on-madness/">A Light on Madness</a></li>                  <li class="active"><a href="/featuredstory/528131/cracking-the-brains-codes/">The Brain’s Codes</a></li>              </ul>
