              <div id="package-custom-stage-content" class="july-2014">
      <div class="spacer"></div>
      <div class="copy">
    <h1>Cracking the Brain’s Codes</h1>
          <p>How does the brain speak to itself?</p>
              <ul class="byline">
  <li>
                  By <a href="/contributor/christof-koch/">Christof Koch</a> and <a href="/contributor/gary-marcus/">Gary Marcus</a> on June 17, 2014                </li>
</ul>          </div>
      <div class="image">
      <img src="http://www.technologyreview.com/sites/default/files/images/brain.codesx480.jpg" width="480" height="607" alt="" />    </div>
    </div>
      
      
            <footer>
      
      
      
